Package org.sat4j

package org.sat4j
Contains a command line launcher for the SAT solvers.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    ILauncherMode
    Allow to change the behavior of the launcher (either decision or optimization mode)
  • Class Summary

    Description

    BasicLauncher<T extends ISolver>

    DecisionMode
    Behavior of the solver when one single solution is needed.
    LightFactory
    That class is the entry point to the default, best performing configuration of SAT4J.
